---
import Title from '~/components/Title.astro'
import Layout from '~/layouts/Layout.astro'
import { getLocale } from '~/utils/i18n'
export { getStaticPaths } from '~/utils/i18n'

const locale = getLocale(Astro)
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Harvest" description="How Harvest handles your data">
  <main class="mx-auto mt-52 w-1/2 pb-24">
    <Title id="privacy-policy" class="xl:text-6xl">Privacy Policy</Title>
    <div class="ml-4 font-bold">Last Updated: February 2026</div>

    <Title class="mt-16 text-4xl font-bold" id="introduction">
      Introduction
    </Title>
    <p>
      Harvest is an autonomous yield farming protocol on Solana. This policy explains how we handle your data.
    </p>
    <div class="mx-12 my-12 flex gap-4 font-bold">
      We don't collect or sell your personal data. Your wallet, your keys, your control.
    </div>

    <Title class="mt-16 text-4xl font-bold" id="1-information-we-do-not-collect">
      1. Information We Do Not Collect
    </Title>
    <p>
      Harvest does not collect any personal information, browsing data, or wallet activity beyond what's publicly visible on the Solana blockchain.
    </p>

    <h3 class="mt-4 text-xl font-bold">
      <strong class="font-bold">1.1 No Personal Data Collection</strong>
    </h3>
    <p>
      We do not collect names, email addresses, IP addresses, or any other personally identifiable information.
    </p>

    <h3 class="mt-4 text-xl font-bold">
      <strong class="font-bold">1.2 No Tracking</strong>
    </h3>
    <p>
      We do not use analytics, advertising networks, or tracking services on our website or protocol.
    </p>

    <Title class="mt-16 text-4xl font-bold" id="2-blockchain-data">
      2. Blockchain Data
    </Title>
    <p>
      All transactions on Harvest are recorded on the Solana blockchain, which is public and immutable. This includes:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong class="font-bold">Deposits and Withdrawals:</strong> Your wallet address and transaction amounts are visible on-chain</li>
      <li><strong class="font-bold">Agent Actions:</strong> Trades and strategy executions performed by our agents are recorded on-chain</li>
      <li><strong class="font-bold">Smart Contract Interactions:</strong> All protocol interactions are publicly verifiable</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-4">
      This is inherent to blockchain technology and not controlled by Harvest.
    </p>

    <Title class="mt-16 text-4xl font-bold" id="3-wallet-connection">
      3. Wallet Connection
    </Title>
    <p>
      When you connect your wallet to Harvest:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Your wallet address is used only to interact with our smart contracts</li>
      <li>We do not store your private keys or seed phrases</li>
      <li>You maintain full custody of your assets at all times</li>
      <li>You can disconnect your wallet at any time</li>
    </ul>

    <Title class="mt-16 text-4xl font-bold" id="4-agent-operations">
      4. Agent Operations
    </Title>
    <p>
      Our AI agents operate autonomously to optimize your yield:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Agents analyze public market data and DeFi protocols</li>
      <li>All agent decisions are executed on-chain and publicly visible</li>
      <li>You can monitor agent activity through your wallet and blockchain explorers</li>
      <li>Agents do not access any personal information</li>
    </ul>

    <Title class="mt-16 text-4xl font-bold" id="5-security">
      5. Security
    </Title>
    <p>
      We take security seriously:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Our smart contracts are audited by reputable security firms</li>
      <li>We use industry-standard security practices</li>
      <li>You maintain full control of your assets through your wallet</li>
      <li>We recommend using hardware wallets for large deposits</li>
    </ul>

    <Title class="mt-16 text-4xl font-bold" id="6-third-party-services">
      6. Third-Party Services
    </Title>
    <p>
      Harvest interacts with various DeFi protocols on Solana. Each protocol has its own terms and risks. We recommend reviewing the documentation of any protocol your funds are deployed to.
    </p>

    <Title class="mt-16 text-4xl font-bold" id="7-website">
      7. Our Website
    </Title>
    <p>
      This website does not use cookies, analytics, or tracking. We may use basic server logs for security and performance monitoring.
    </p>

    <Title class="mt-16 text-4xl font-bold" id="8-changes">
      8. Changes to This Policy
    </Title>
    <p>
      We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.
    </p>

    <Title class="mt-16 text-4xl font-bold" id="9-contact">
      9. Contact Us
    </Title>
    <p>
      If you have questions about this privacy policy, reach us on X at @harvest_bot.
    </p>
  </main>
</Layout>
<style>
  p,
  li {
    @apply opacity-55;
  }

  ul {
    @apply mt-4;
  }

  li {
    @apply ml-4 list-disc;
  }
</style>
